Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让它陷入了静寂而永恒的睡眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个森林即使是现在仍然遍布着坚硬的荆棘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地阻止着来自外部的侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.05,0:00:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 会持续到我死亡的时候为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.19,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人她…？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试结束后就是圣诞节呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.62,0:02:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄蔷薇大人说结业式时要在蔷薇馆开个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要包装吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是流言中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是放弃读这本书比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳怎么想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话 会读的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面也有些在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.92,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先单纯地读读看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.11,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样去读 如果白蔷薇大人的事真写在上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须加星如果是白蔷薇大人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我会更加尊敬她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会请她在文集上签名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错啊 你的这种性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 果然对是否读这本书犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书的作者“须加星”实际上是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那个白蔷薇大人出版了将自已\n隐藏的过去毫不隐瞒地拼缀起来的自白小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种流言在到处流传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说也只是流言而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.41,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看过这本叫“大波斯菊通信”的\n新刊导读杂志上专题介绍的人们的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者 须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园里数月的生活是否只是梦幻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣将一切封印在了心中那荆棘的森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待的新人作家 冲击的自传性处女作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.85,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须加星与白蔷薇大人的真名“佐藤圣”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确“星”与“圣”发音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既然是自传性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是将自已的过去写在了这本小说里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会流言四起也是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人过去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一年级生的由乃你们大概不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人的过去也可说是禁忌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都尽量不去提及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说是一种“无言的理解”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道事情的人大家都三缄其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在保护着什么似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.31,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我是一年级生 没有被告知详细的经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.46,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去… 是去年的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.14,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个白蔷薇大人的过去写在了这本书里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人会犹豫也是不无道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.06,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 大人们想强制把互为挚友的圣与香织分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是她们在圣诞夜里踏上了没有目的地的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她们两人想一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当圣在病院里醒过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织已经去往天国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很常见的结局嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.22,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学 你看到最后都没哭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有些地方和我与祥子大人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.66,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 想说的不是小说的内容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确看了这个后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有流言说作者是白蔷薇大人倒也可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小说的舞台只可能是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 令虽然也看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就说“不要再插手这件事”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“就当没有读过这本小说”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“完全不想与流言有任何关联”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 祥子大人在买了文集后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉也是对读还是不读犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令什么也不肯对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 只有直接去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是只有去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 志摩子同学也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…？ 你们不是姐妹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就去比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.37,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话 白蔷薇大人就会去蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在令大人与祥子大人面前问不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级藤组 佐藤圣同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻到生活指导室来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是因为那本小说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 佑巳也被传唤了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是佑巳将我作为“搂抱魔”告发了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人 您还不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我本来还想问您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“荆棘的森林”的作者\n是否就是白蔷薇大人您或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.94,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荆棘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去的话一会儿再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.76,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 中高等部校长 年级主任以及藤组的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“荆棘的森林”已经变成这么严重的问题了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.26,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟往常一样开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像还不知道被传唤的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.75,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是值得告诉新闻部的东西 我们可是一点儿也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人退学也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的学园可是禁止打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写小说什么的明显是违反了校规啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退学什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情变成那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用“莉莉安瓦版”来发起署名活动也无所谓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写上“请不要将白蔷薇大人退学”什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们真的什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法再支撑下去了 快站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在生活指导室里互相抱着摔在一起可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打扰到各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到\n大家无法抑制的好奇心我还是先报告一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 写“荆棘的森林”的人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 这一次不能向\n莉莉安瓦版提供新闻材料真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筑山三奈子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概大家听到传唤的广播后都在等我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当华丽的传唤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是从没有因个人的事情而被传唤过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有点羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是蔷薇大人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没像我这样慌里慌张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了生活指导室吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上等品真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先报告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经向佑巳与由乃说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言中的那本小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被传唤的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚地说明不是我写的之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长为我说了好话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后简单地就让我离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已既没有读过实物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.83,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对于那个流传的谣言也是刚才才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你写的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向圣母玛莉亚发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个话题就到此结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？ 黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议 红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 该讨论一下圣诞节的联欢会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都未受到流言的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是自我中心又浅薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我脸上的表情又变来变去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想发言吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡得迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见的人要好好地举起手来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟会为了这种人而烦恼真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.59,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 在闹情绪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 把佑巳借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会脱她的制服或是胡来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再开玩笑的话 我可要拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令 把由乃也借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要由乃愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么痛快就允诺没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为令明白我不会对由乃淘气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那为什么只对我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为反应很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 祥子的反应也很让人开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是一次捉弄就会有双倍乐趣的姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:13:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我成了坏心前辈的饵食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 后面的收拾就由我们三人来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么后面就拜讬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.73,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 不要让白蔷薇大人太开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 有需要我帮忙的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看起来也没什么需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们陪着姐姐真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让志摩子同学跟我们在一起不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子是那种即使跟她说不要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她想留下来就会凭自已的意志留下来的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在带着那本“荆棘的森林”吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借我一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借倒是没什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是读它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你以为我会拿它当锅垫吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.73,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么做为回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面食堂的餐券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候在自动贩卖机那里帮我买一罐咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你们的份也一起买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人真是个不可预料的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同学真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能和那种人做姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在颈上围上手帕比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣领会弄脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.19,0:15:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.99,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.56,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人究竟是为了什么将我们留下来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 如果只是为了借“荆棘的森林”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接带回家去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.41,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为我们太可爱 所以想要请我们吃拉面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 脑筋快成豆腐渣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说是不会买罐装年糕豆汤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 那个罐装年糕豆汤什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上还有这种东西存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 白蔷薇大人要的咖啡我们可是好好地买来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把书仔细地读完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.85,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为“荆棘的森林”是我写的\N那些人也许真是有很好的直觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不是跟我很像吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想问也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会认为写那本小说的是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是名字同音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你们也应该有些发觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.84,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们毫不掩饰地流露出了那种好奇心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是为了看你们这种表情才说这种话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的部份我不会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也没问题的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.79,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.28,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为总觉得只有你们不知道不是很不公平吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了告诉我们才将我们留下来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也是为了想早点读到这本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓉子与令她们之所以不向你们说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也许是为了体谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么痛苦的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有过一个非常要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说她甚至比父母和兄弟更加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢她到只要有她在 其它什么也不需要的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个想着将来成为修女的纯洁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在去年的圣诞节里 她离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全是“荆棘的森林”的圣与香织嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是完全相同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既没有与那个朋友一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有吞下安眠药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她转学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说香织还活着了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 还活着很失望吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.68,0:18:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 难道是谁以白蔷薇大人\N的事作为参考而写下了这本小说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.83,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有不同的部份 也有相似得惊人的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得生气吗 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已的过去被擅自写成了小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.68,0:18:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被人误认为是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.90,0:18:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只要能被最重要的人理解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想讲给你们俩听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我讨厌残留着误解与臆测的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学的朋友 现在怎么样了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎么样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想见她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不见面 为好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的名字 不是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是久保 栞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人现在还喜欢着那个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才没有留下志摩子同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会对志摩子同学很过意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不可原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明会有因小说而受到伤害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写那本小说的不会是久保栞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.37,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会彻底查明写这本“荆棘的森林”的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是大波斯菊编辑部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把我也拉来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令也很在意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“荆棘的森林”的作者到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉在忙碌的时候来打扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 你是“荆棘的森林”的负责人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不能将须加星的真实身份告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.19,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天 来自莉莉安学生们的询问接连不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“须加星的真实身份是否是佐藤圣”之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.63,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真令人怀念啊 这种制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到会在这种地方遇到后辈们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.73,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.98,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这么说您是莉莉安的毕业生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是很久以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本名是春日诚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.28,0:21:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么“荆棘的森林”的舞台果然是莉莉安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前发生的事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“荆棘的森林”是在如今\n连传闻都未留下的很久以前发生的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.17,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟白蔷薇大人的故事就像是其它的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有从嘴里说出她的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.51,0:21:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今年开始进入莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.68,0:22:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 花瓣的瓣是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.23,0:23:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个“瓣”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是拘泥在一些古怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣的瓣写成汉字就是便当的“便”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.54,topfont,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：日语中花瓣的“瓣”与便当的“便”同形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当的“便”吗 原来如此 是便当的“便”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周明明是个好故事 真觉得有点被糟塌啦
